Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd overwhelm the band and crush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:03.69,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(192,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&HC2C1B1&\3c&HBF7051&\bord2\pos(175,66.5)\frz22.62}Sob
